WEBVTT

1
00:00:47.089 --> 00:00:49.759 line:80%
This place sucks whenever I come here.

2
00:00:59.185 --> 00:01:01.979 line:80%
I'm Prosecutor Choi Tae-su
from Criminal Division 3.

3
00:01:09.445 --> 00:01:14.033 line:80%
You were born with a silver spoon.
You're pretty and probably well-mannered.

4
00:01:15.117 --> 00:01:18.454 line:80%
Everyone treats you nicely,
so nothing's hard for you.

5
00:01:22.166 --> 00:01:23.918 line:80%
But things are different now.

6
00:01:26.212 --> 00:01:28.923 line:80%
Everyone thinks
this is just a formality, but...

7
00:01:29.006 --> 00:01:32.092 line:80%
It is.
This investigation is just a formality.

8
00:01:34.762 --> 00:01:36.472 line:80%
Look here, Ms. Oh Yu-ra!

9
00:01:36.555 --> 00:01:38.057 line:80%
Look here, Prosecutor!

10
00:01:39.475 --> 00:01:42.186 line:80%
It's not the time for a mere prosecutor
to act up.

11
00:01:42.269 --> 00:01:46.899 line:80%
Do I look like a fool who'd be scared
after seeing you rush in here?

12
00:01:51.529 --> 00:01:53.364 line:80%
You're not sure about anything.

13
00:01:59.245 --> 00:02:03.332 line:80%
Would it be faster for me to say
what you want to hear out of fear,

14
00:02:04.124 --> 00:02:07.169 line:80%
or to get out of here on my own?

15
00:02:11.507 --> 00:02:12.758 line:80%
Do you want to bet?

16
00:02:32.403 --> 00:02:34.113 line:80%
-Goodbye, ma'am!
-Goodbye, ma'am!

17
00:02:41.412 --> 00:02:43.289 line:80%
The world must be going crazy.

18
00:02:43.372 --> 00:02:46.458 line:80%
Everyone keeps crossing the line.

19
00:02:47.585 --> 00:02:51.672 line:80%
This is for the best.
They can't do anything with that file.

20
00:03:05.769 --> 00:03:09.648 line:80%
You didn't have to come here.

21
00:03:10.441 --> 00:03:12.818 line:80%
There was a misunderstanding.

22
00:03:13.611 --> 00:03:17.531 line:80%
I guess I'm not a great judge
of character.

23
00:03:17.615 --> 00:03:18.657 line:80%
Oh Yu-ra.

24
00:03:20.951 --> 00:03:22.786 line:80%
You crossed the line this time.

25
00:03:24.705 --> 00:03:26.206 line:80%
Turn in your resignation.

26
00:03:27.666 --> 00:03:32.212 line:80%
Don't think about exercising your rights
over the airline and tour company shares.

27
00:03:33.672 --> 00:03:34.924 line:80%
Soon,

28
00:03:35.007 --> 00:03:38.844 line:80%
U&K Foundation will send
a volunteer group to Africa. Join them.

29
00:03:38.928 --> 00:03:42.389 line:80%
Go and volunteer and volunteer some more.

30
00:03:43.265 --> 00:03:48.771 line:80%
And once you've built character,
you can return then.

31
00:03:49.813 --> 00:03:52.733 line:80%
I gave you the position,
and it ruined you.

32
00:03:55.027 --> 00:03:58.364 line:80%
Still, it's a big privilege
to have another chance.

33
00:03:58.948 --> 00:04:00.199 line:80%
Keep that in mind.

34
00:04:03.327 --> 00:04:04.286 line:80%
No.

35
00:04:06.705 --> 00:04:10.125 line:80%
Why would I resign?
Why should I volunteer?

36
00:04:11.210 --> 00:04:12.711 line:80%
Africa?

37
00:04:15.881 --> 00:04:20.094 line:80%
Right. You must like her. Don't you?

38
00:04:21.095 --> 00:04:26.058 line:80%
Ji-hyuk is family after all,
so you want to let him do what he wants.

39
00:04:32.690 --> 00:04:33.899 line:80%
Do it, then.

40
00:04:39.446 --> 00:04:41.865 line:80%
But don't touch me.

41
00:04:41.949 --> 00:04:43.784 line:80%
What did I do wrong?

42
00:04:44.368 --> 00:04:47.079 line:80%
You're pretending to be fair.

43
00:04:48.163 --> 00:04:49.456 line:80%
But you're not.

44
00:05:04.972 --> 00:05:08.600 line:80%
I told him it'd be no use,
but he didn't know you at all.

45
00:05:10.811 --> 00:05:12.563 line:80%
What the hell are you saying?

46
00:05:14.815 --> 00:05:16.984 line:80%
I'm exhausted. Let's talk tomorrow.

47
00:05:18.861 --> 00:05:21.155 line:80%
You shouldn't have messed with Ji-won.

48
00:05:25.951 --> 00:05:26.910 line:80%
What?

49
00:05:28.078 --> 00:05:29.788 line:80%
What did I do?

50
00:05:29.872 --> 00:05:34.251 line:80%
No. Even if I did do something,
do you have proof?

51
00:05:35.586 --> 00:05:36.587 line:80%
Yes.

52
00:05:38.380 --> 00:05:39.423 line:80%
I do.

53
00:06:07.826 --> 00:06:10.329 line:80%
What's wrong? Did you see a ghost?

54
00:06:12.956 --> 00:06:14.249 line:80%
What do I have to do?

55
00:06:14.958 --> 00:06:16.794 line:80%
Tell me what I don't know.

56
00:06:26.095 --> 00:06:27.888 line:80%
-Are you crazy?
-Hurry!

57
00:06:44.696 --> 00:06:46.115 line:80%
Pay for what you did.

58
00:06:47.199 --> 00:06:50.327 line:80%
Your problem is thinking
you can do anything you want.

59
00:06:51.203 --> 00:06:53.122 line:80%
Stop trying to get away with it.

60
00:06:53.789 --> 00:06:54.957 line:80%
Pay properly.

61
00:06:56.041 --> 00:06:57.709 line:80%
Jeong Man-sik, Bae Hui-suk.

62
00:06:57.793 --> 00:07:00.754 line:80%
You're under arrest for attempted murder.

63
00:07:00.838 --> 00:07:05.050 line:80%
Yeah, yeah.
I'll tell you everything. Everything.

64
00:07:10.514 --> 00:07:14.935 line:80%
Now that Jeong Man-sik's showed up,
I'd like to talk to you again, Ms. Oh.

65
00:07:50.053 --> 00:07:51.263 line:80%
Mom!

66
00:07:52.264 --> 00:07:54.474 line:80%
-Ju-ran.
-Princess.

67
00:08:45.150 --> 00:08:46.151 line:80%
Goodness.

68
00:08:46.818 --> 00:08:49.321 line:80%
Jeong Su-min did something like that?

69
00:08:52.491 --> 00:08:57.204 line:80%
Mr. Park's funeral was held
just downstairs, but I had no idea.

70
00:08:57.871 --> 00:08:59.414 line:80%
It feels strange.

71
00:09:00.040 --> 00:09:02.000 line:80%
If I had known, I would have--

72
00:09:02.084 --> 00:09:03.877 line:80%
You still shouldn't have.

73
00:09:04.711 --> 00:09:07.839 line:80%
You can't go to a funeral
before a major surgery.

74
00:09:10.759 --> 00:09:12.511 line:80%
You're nagging again.

75
00:09:12.594 --> 00:09:14.429 line:80%
The surgery went well.

76
00:09:14.513 --> 00:09:16.598 line:80%
Because the surgery went well.

77
00:09:16.682 --> 00:09:20.143 line:80%
You got scared and cried before.
Shall I keep going?

78
00:09:22.354 --> 00:09:25.816 line:80%
Anyway, since the SD card's data
was recovered,

79
00:09:25.899 --> 00:09:27.276 line:80%
things got easier.

80
00:09:28.277 --> 00:09:32.656 line:80%
The court will take recent threats
into account seriously as well.

81
00:09:33.240 --> 00:09:34.366 line:80%
It'll all work out.

82
00:09:34.866 --> 00:09:38.537 line:80%
You might be able to get
both parental rights and custody.

83
00:09:39.413 --> 00:09:42.833 line:80%
Well, let's make him
lose visitation rights as well.

84
00:09:43.959 --> 00:09:49.381 line:80%
Then Yeon-ji will lose his father
for good.

85
00:09:56.054 --> 00:09:59.057 line:80%
You don't have to if you don't want to.

86
00:10:00.851 --> 00:10:04.896 line:80%
The choice is yours.

87
00:10:07.274 --> 00:10:08.859 line:80%
I'm happy about it.

88
00:10:16.867 --> 00:10:18.243 line:80%
When I got the surgery,

89
00:10:20.120 --> 00:10:22.414 line:80%
it felt like I was dying once.

90
00:10:25.625 --> 00:10:27.044 line:80%
Do I look like a bum?

91
00:10:27.127 --> 00:10:28.378 line:80%
Do I play all day?

92
00:10:28.462 --> 00:10:31.590 line:80%
I couldn't see the end, so it was so hard.

93
00:10:34.009 --> 00:10:35.260 line:80%
Stop it!

94
00:10:37.512 --> 00:10:40.015 line:80%
I was even betrayed.

95
00:10:46.605 --> 00:10:47.522 line:80%
But...

96
00:10:49.775 --> 00:10:51.610 line:80%
I got a new chance.

97
00:10:59.534 --> 00:11:01.244 line:80%
Lee Jae-won, that bastard.

98
00:11:02.454 --> 00:11:05.040 line:80%
He'll probably try to milk Yeon-ji later.

99
00:11:05.874 --> 00:11:07.709 line:80%
He'll never be helpful for her.

100
00:11:09.252 --> 00:11:11.421 line:80%
I can't let her suffer like that.

101
00:11:11.963 --> 00:11:13.715 line:80%
He's nothing but a birth father.

102
00:11:16.635 --> 00:11:17.761 line:80%
I...

103
00:11:19.638 --> 00:11:21.598 line:80%
will stay strong.

104
00:11:23.517 --> 00:11:26.645 line:80%
I'll try a little harder too.

105
00:11:45.205 --> 00:11:48.041 line:80%
FINAL EPISODE

106
00:12:10.313 --> 00:12:12.149 line:80%
God, you scared me.

107
00:12:14.151 --> 00:12:16.528 line:80%
I'm sorry. I was just happy to see you.

108
00:12:18.655 --> 00:12:23.577 line:80%
Well, Ji-won wanted to finalize
the factory manufacturing recipe today.

109
00:12:23.660 --> 00:12:27.080 line:80%
She wanted to discuss that.
That's why I came.

110
00:12:27.831 --> 00:12:29.082 line:80%
Did she go somewhere?

111
00:12:29.166 --> 00:12:33.170 line:80%
Ms. Kang's meeting with
the development team is running late.

112
00:12:34.087 --> 00:12:37.757 line:80%
Sorry to disappoint you, but I'll explain.
Follow me this way.

113
00:12:43.513 --> 00:12:47.058 line:80%
The spinach pasta with sea snails,
the perilla cream pasta,

114
00:12:47.142 --> 00:12:50.812 line:80%
and the sweet pumpkin soup.
Please check the recipes again.

115
00:12:50.896 --> 00:12:53.482 line:80%
Also...

116
00:12:54.149 --> 00:12:58.778 line:80%
By the way,
did I do something wrong to you?

117
00:12:59.613 --> 00:13:00.697 line:80%
What?

118
00:13:01.364 --> 00:13:04.284 line:80%
I mean,
you weren't here when I came last time.

119
00:13:04.784 --> 00:13:08.622 line:80%
And you're being kind of unfriendly today.

120
00:13:10.332 --> 00:13:11.583 line:80%
I'm happy to see you.

121
00:13:13.919 --> 00:13:17.923 line:80%
I'm clueless,
so I wouldn't know if you don't tell me.

122
00:13:19.549 --> 00:13:23.595 line:80%
So if I did something wrong, I'm sorry.

123
00:13:25.639 --> 00:13:27.057 line:80%
Even if didn't, I'm sorry.

124
00:13:28.892 --> 00:13:31.061 line:80%
Did you notice I was away?

125
00:13:31.144 --> 00:13:32.354 line:80%
Of course.

126
00:13:32.896 --> 00:13:34.147 line:80%
I looked for you.

127
00:13:36.191 --> 00:13:37.359 line:80%
Why would you?

128
00:13:38.735 --> 00:13:39.653 line:80%
What?

129
00:13:42.239 --> 00:13:43.573 line:80%
Well...

130
00:13:43.657 --> 00:13:48.828 line:80%
Right. I brought a Basque cake I made
last time and the time before.

131
00:13:49.412 --> 00:13:50.664 line:80%
Because...

132
00:13:52.249 --> 00:13:55.460 line:80%
I remembered how you loved it.

133
00:13:55.544 --> 00:13:58.338 line:80%
Who's the person
that sent such a great cake?

134
00:13:58.421 --> 00:14:00.549 line:80%
This is love itself!

135
00:14:02.509 --> 00:14:06.137 line:80%
I bought a new oven,
and it's insanely good, you know.

136
00:14:06.221 --> 00:14:11.101 line:80%
So whatever dish I make,
it tastes three times as good.

137
00:14:11.601 --> 00:14:14.729 line:80%
I guess it's why I kept cooking.

138
00:14:15.772 --> 00:14:17.607 line:80%
By the way, your ears...

139
00:14:18.358 --> 00:14:19.985 line:80%
are so big and pretty.

140
00:14:21.486 --> 00:14:24.322 line:80%
What are you doing?

141
00:14:25.949 --> 00:14:28.868 line:80%
You can't touch someone's ear like that.

142
00:14:29.744 --> 00:14:31.329 line:80%
Why not?

143
00:14:31.997 --> 00:14:34.124 line:80%
What? I don't know.

144
00:14:34.207 --> 00:14:36.209 line:80%
But you can't do it.

145
00:14:36.710 --> 00:14:38.420 line:80%
Can I touch your hands, then?

146
00:14:38.503 --> 00:14:42.257 line:80%
Of course. You can touch my hands,
but my ears are sensitive...

147
00:14:58.231 --> 00:15:00.900 line:80%
I think I like you.

148
00:15:02.235 --> 00:15:03.194 line:80%
What?

149
00:15:27.177 --> 00:15:29.512 line:80%
When it comes to life,

150
00:15:29.596 --> 00:15:32.098 line:80%
you can't have both.

151
00:15:33.183 --> 00:15:34.225 line:80%
What I mean is,

152
00:15:34.976 --> 00:15:37.812 line:80%
as long as he inherits U&K,

153
00:15:37.896 --> 00:15:40.315 line:80%
it won't be easy to harmonize

154
00:15:40.982 --> 00:15:45.403 line:80%
your personal happiness
and his social responsibilities.

155
00:15:52.661 --> 00:15:53.495 line:80%
What?

156
00:15:55.455 --> 00:15:57.082 line:80%
It's just that...

157
00:15:57.165 --> 00:16:02.379 line:80%
The way you speak is
very similar to the way Ji-hyuk does.

158
00:16:05.173 --> 00:16:07.676 line:80%
He does talk kind of like Grandfather.

159
00:16:11.096 --> 00:16:12.847 line:80%
See! Look at that!

160
00:16:13.348 --> 00:16:16.309 line:80%
See! They have the same tastes!
Look at their pick.

161
00:16:16.393 --> 00:16:18.395 line:80%
I'm disappointed in you, Grandfather.

162
00:16:23.233 --> 00:16:25.777 line:80%
I'll try very hard.

163
00:16:27.696 --> 00:16:31.032 line:80%
I know I was given a precious opportunity.

164
00:16:31.700 --> 00:16:36.246 line:80%
I'll make sure to be less greedy
and more generous in life.

165
00:16:38.707 --> 00:16:40.417 line:80%
Do you think it's that easy?

166
00:16:42.460 --> 00:16:43.878 line:80%
If it doesn't work...

167
00:16:48.842 --> 00:16:50.385 line:80%
I'll try harder!

168
00:17:02.939 --> 00:17:04.858 line:80%
Can I continue eating now?

169
00:17:04.941 --> 00:17:07.861 line:80%
Sure, eat up.
I guess I spoke for too long.

170
00:17:11.406 --> 00:17:13.283 line:80%
I'm sorry. I talked too much.

171
00:17:28.631 --> 00:17:29.841 line:80%
Thank you.

172
00:17:30.467 --> 00:17:33.261 line:80%
Now, let's toast to Chef Eun-ho's success!

173
00:17:33.344 --> 00:17:35.221 line:80%
And to a successful divorce!

174
00:17:35.764 --> 00:17:37.807 line:80%
And to successful love! Let's go!

175
00:17:37.891 --> 00:17:39.267 line:80%
Cheers!

176
00:17:46.399 --> 00:17:48.318 line:80%
Beer tastes the best this way.

177
00:17:49.319 --> 00:17:53.907 line:80%
Don't be surprised. This must be
his first time eating food like this.

178
00:17:53.990 --> 00:17:58.286 line:80%
What are you talking about? He eats
pork
gukbap
with tons of
jeongguji
.

179
00:18:01.915 --> 00:18:04.667 line:80%
Tons of what? What's that?

180
00:18:05.543 --> 00:18:08.838 line:80%
She doesn't know what it is.
It's no use talking to her.

181
00:18:08.922 --> 00:18:10.256 line:80%
You're right.

182
00:18:12.884 --> 00:18:16.638 line:80%
I really feel like
I came back from the dead.

183
00:18:17.347 --> 00:18:20.850 line:80%
I'm surprised by you two,
but how are you two siblings?

184
00:18:22.519 --> 00:18:24.229 line:80%
They don't look alike at all.

185
00:18:25.480 --> 00:18:27.982 line:80%
What? You said we did!

186
00:18:28.066 --> 00:18:29.526 line:80%
-I did?
-Yeah.

187
00:18:29.609 --> 00:18:31.611 line:80%
-When?
-You don't remember?

188
00:18:34.906 --> 00:18:38.117 line:80%
It's strange that you're here too,
Mr. Lee.

189
00:18:40.036 --> 00:18:43.623 line:80%
Let me be clear.
I'm not here for you, Ms. Yang.

190
00:18:43.706 --> 00:18:47.460 line:80%
-I work for the U&K family--
-Yes. That's what I meant.

191
00:18:48.920 --> 00:18:53.883 line:80%
You're an incredible person
to the U&K family.

192
00:18:55.009 --> 00:18:57.637 line:80%
But Mr. Yu is a member of the family,

193
00:18:58.179 --> 00:19:01.766 line:80%
thus you're here. That's very surprising.

194
00:19:06.563 --> 00:19:09.107 line:80%
Wait, am I being too comfortable now?

195
00:19:10.233 --> 00:19:14.279 line:80%
I'm part of the owner's family too.

196
00:19:14.362 --> 00:19:19.659 line:80%
Also, Mr. Lee wouldn't come to an occasion
like this even if the owner told him to--

197
00:19:23.371 --> 00:19:27.500 line:80%
It's part of my job to make sure
the owner's family watch what they say.

198
00:19:35.425 --> 00:19:37.343 line:80%
Is he always like that?

199
00:19:44.392 --> 00:19:45.476 line:80%
It's so good.

200
00:19:45.560 --> 00:19:47.103 line:80%
We ordered everything in.

201
00:19:48.479 --> 00:19:50.648 line:80%
-Bye.
-Get home safe.

202
00:19:50.732 --> 00:19:51.774 line:80%
It's raining.

203
00:19:56.029 --> 00:19:57.822 line:80%
What do we do?

204
00:19:57.906 --> 00:20:00.158 line:80%
We only have two umbrellas.

205
00:20:00.241 --> 00:20:02.327 line:80%
I drove here, so I'm good.

206
00:20:04.370 --> 00:20:06.247 line:80%
It's on my way...

207
00:20:09.542 --> 00:20:11.461 line:80%
What's on your way?

208
00:20:12.086 --> 00:20:15.006 line:80%
If you mean my home,
you could give me a ride.

209
00:20:17.508 --> 00:20:20.178 line:80%
I can just run and catch the bus.

210
00:20:20.261 --> 00:20:24.474 line:80%
Why don't I give you a ride?
If that's okay with you.

211
00:20:24.557 --> 00:20:26.351 line:80%
It's the opposite direction.

212
00:20:29.896 --> 00:20:31.356 line:80%
Shall I?

213
00:20:31.439 --> 00:20:32.440 line:80%
That works out.

214
00:20:33.858 --> 00:20:35.068 line:80%
The elevator's here.

215
00:20:37.320 --> 00:20:39.364 line:80%
Thanks for coming today.

216
00:20:39.447 --> 00:20:40.531 line:80%
Get home safe.

217
00:20:40.615 --> 00:20:42.283 line:80%
Have a good rest, Ms. Kang.

218
00:20:43.076 --> 00:20:45.286 line:80%
And Ji-hyuk, you rest or whatever.

219
00:20:50.458 --> 00:20:53.920 line:80%
But why are
Eun-ho and Hui-yeon going together?

220
00:20:54.003 --> 00:20:57.715 line:80%
And toasted for successful love.
What was that about?

221
00:20:57.799 --> 00:21:00.051 line:80%
My goodness, you're so clueless.

222
00:21:02.387 --> 00:21:03.388 line:80%
I'm going in.

223
00:21:07.392 --> 00:21:10.728 line:80%
Eun-ho likes Hui-yeon? Why?

224
00:21:11.854 --> 00:21:14.482 line:80%
I don't understand.

225
00:22:21.758 --> 00:22:23.051 line:80%
Be careful.

226
00:23:04.842 --> 00:23:06.052 line:80%
What are you doing?

227
00:23:07.804 --> 00:23:09.013 line:80%
Are you up?

228
00:23:10.306 --> 00:23:12.558 line:80%
It would've been better
to stay unconscious.

229
00:23:19.482 --> 00:23:21.776 line:80%
Fire spreads more because of curtains.

230
00:23:23.402 --> 00:23:25.446 line:80%
